snippet.title: Aperture Fight Focused
snippet.description:
Aperture broadcasts free martial arts tutorial videos covering JiuJitsu, Muay Thai, Boxing, Filipino Kali and more!  Our guests include UFC fighters, coaches, martial arts experts, and defensive tactics professionals from law enforcement, military and civilian sectors!

You can learn so much more about Aperture Fight Focused by visiting our website at www.ApertureFightFocused.com which links to our library of martial arts and self defense at www.Aperture.University
